Building off of the Borel sets, welet \Sigma _0 denote open sets, \Pi _0 the closed sets, and then 
\Sigma _n =  \{ \bigcup _i^ \omega  A_i : A_i  \in   \Pi _{n-1} \}
\Pi _n =  \{ \bigcap _i^ \omega  A_i : A_i  \in   \Sigma _{n-1} \}

